rows.label: qst102206_msg0001
rows.name:
P-please! Help!
You have to save the chief!

rows.label: qst102206_msg0002
rows.name:
The two Brutal Aspid...they attacked
us out of nowhere...

rows.label: qst102206_msg0003
rows.name:
Our formation was in tatters, and
we all wound up separated!

rows.label: qst102206_msg0004
rows.name:
Corden said he'd buy some time so I
could get away and find you guys, but
I don't know how long he'll hold out!

rows.label: qst102206_msg0005
rows.name:
You've gotta save the others!
Please!

rows.label: qst102206_msg0006
rows.name:
Last I saw, they were in the Chamber
of Pillars on the cavern's lowest level.

rows.label: qst102206_msg0007
rows.name:
I'll grab some spare weapons and
then head right after you!

rows.label: qst102206_msg0101
rows.name:
The squad was attacked in the
Chamber of Pillars, on the lowest level.

rows.label: qst102206_msg0102
rows.name:
The ground's pretty precarious,
so be careful down there!
